summary:
I am passionate about building bridges through effective change management. Also, I find fascinating the relationship between culture, people and business desired outcomes. 

What can you expect from me as a professional? A collaborations spark that makes an impact on international organizations with intercultural management, relationship building, proactive communication, and adaptability to challenging organizational contexts.

What can you expect from me as a person? A smile to brighten up, an ear to listen, a shoulder to support but also structure, candid feedback, and lots of fun.
